{"tid":1941483,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"(一人一個)家母之黑暗料理","createTime":"2020-03-24T12:24:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-25T11:30:40.000Z","uid":74965,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c94ce2f80409cffe3bd6d9cba7e1573e387238fd","tid":1941483,"uid":74965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T12:24:53.000Z","msg":"拋磚先<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/82VxoHo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F82VxoHo.jpg&h=71deb691&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我知大家都食過好多老母自創奇形怪狀既野<br />\n我都食唔少<br />\n但依樣我真係頂唔順要拎出黎<br />\n食一啖苦到即刻嘔出黎<br />\n我乜係問野菜黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢話我知<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">係艾草黎，好健康架</span><br />\n<br />\n我頂一聲，我剩係聽過艾草用黎浸腳、 <br />\n敷藥，未聽過可以煮湯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n諗起就想繼續嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0384def925c1ca07fa2ed210688ccf3e2d165ea","tid":1941483,"uid":198315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c94ce2f80409cffe3bd6d9cba7e1573e387238fd","tid":1941483,"uid":74965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T12:24:53.000Z","msg":"拋磚先<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/82VxoHo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F82VxoHo.jpg&h=71deb691&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我知大家都食過好多老母自創奇形怪狀既野<br />\n我都食唔少<br />\n但依樣我真係頂唔順要拎出黎<br />\n食一啖苦到即刻嘔出黎<br />\n我乜係問野菜黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"h